        "column_jCLTXx": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled-10.png",
            "title": "★★★★★",
            "text": "<h6>The quality of the hat I received is outstanding it's well-made, comfortable, and perfect for both sunny days and chilly evenings. The material feels durable and the craftsmanship is top-notch.</h6><p><strong>Richal</strong></p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_MHrEix": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled-8.png",
            "title": "★★★★★",
            "text": "<h6>I ordered a stylish fedora for my husband and a chic sun hat for myself. Both arrived quickly and exceeded our expectations. The fit was perfect, and the materials felt luxurious. It's clear that Ralter M lakes pride in curating a collection of hats that are both fashionable and well made.</h6><p><strong>Olivia</strong></p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_gXjjLa": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled-2.png",
            "title": "★★★★★",
            "text": "<h6>after M Hat Company, and I couldn't be more thrilled with my experience! Their selection of men's and women's hats is impressive, offering everything from classic fedoras to trendy wide brimmed styles. The quality of the hats is top notch, with excellent craftsmanship and al tention to detail.</h6><p><strong>Ammi</strong></p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
      },
